    },
    "DiskCleaner 需要完全磁盘访问，才能扫描系统各处的缓存、日志和大文件。这项权限只能由你在系统设置中手动授予。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "DiskCleaner needs Full Disk Access to scan caches, logs, and large files across the system. This permission can only be granted manually in System Settings."
          }
        }
      }
    },
